item.title: Ufos
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

[quote=“ninja nub, post:15, topic:201247”][quote author=jme link=topic=265906.msg2199332#msg2199332 date=1208680058]
I still think there is probably explanations, but I’ve seen some creepy shit in the skies twice. Sober I think… either way a lot of people saw it.
[/quote]

This is coming from who :rolleyes:?

Lol, this is just going to lead to that extraterrestrial shit in discussion and debates section.[/quote]

I was sober and everyone in town saw it.

It was night time, there were large lights spinning around and it was moving in the sky far faster then any airplanes could go. Saw something similar a few nights after.

The town I was in also has a history of weird things. The entire staff at the wood mill there claim to have seen a UFO land in the mill. It was very small and when they approached it, it shot back up in the sky. This was 10 years ago though, and I don’t know anything about it. Personally I don’t believe it ever happened.

I never really believed in UFO’s before, but if you saw those sightings, it would really confuse you for what the hell else it could be. I would like to believe there is a logical explanation though.

Read full topic
